{"id":340684,"date":[{"year":1957,"month":1,"day":16}],"page":"1","source":"本报","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"","column":"","genre":"","count":"138","ytitle":"","mtitle":"忽如一夜春风来　千树万树梨花开","ftitle":"","authors":[],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入3号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1957\\01\\571g011301.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>昨晨七时廿一分，上海忽下冰粒，到十时三十四分大雪纷飞，全市顿成银装世界。这次下雪六厘米，是1958年2月以来上海又一次大雪。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上图为苏州河上河滨公园雪景。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"【本报记者　康正平摄】</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入3号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1957\\01\\571g011302.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>下图为托儿所的小朋友们在玩雪。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"【本报记者钟志仁摄】</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgaut>康正平</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgaut>钟志仁</FONT>"}]}